# LCD Screen Code
This is the code for the on board LCD screen to show status of different things withouth geting inside the RPI directly, very usefull for hardware people to trouble shoot stuff

# LCD on startup
There is a startup scipt that should run every time. If it doesnet try going to:
vortex-auv/scripts/
and execute script that adds our LCD screen srit into the bootup sequence:
add_LCD_service_file_to_bootup_sequence.sh